room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Adventure" by To Escape in Lawrence
review: Really interesting and unique puzzles. Had a really good time working through them.

room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Adventure" by To Escape in Lawrence
review: This escape room was awesome! We have done about 40 rooms mostly in Kansas and Missouri. Some of them have been really cool... but this one is the best! Don't let the small town fool you, this is a high-quality room! Super impressed!

room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Adventure" by To Escape in Lawrence
review: I had never done one of these so it was a new adventure. Very fun! A lot of thought was put into this room. I recommend it to anyone looking for an hour of fun.

room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Adventure" by To Escape in Lawrence
review: This escape room was great! I have been to about 6 escape rooms now and this was by far one of the most creative and fun rooms I have been in! Anyone in the greater KC area that likes escape rooms should make sure they pay this one a visit! It was well worth the drive!

room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Adventure" by To Escape in Lawrence
review: This room was so intricate and detailed I was genuinely surprised at how great this room flowed together! Anyone who has a thrill for adventure, puzzles, and escape rooms should check this one out!
